description:
The objective of this module is to develop the learning

capabilities and hone the problem solving skills of talented

students at a mathematically deeper and more rigorous

level. The contents of this module will consist of those in

the regular module (MA3111 Complex Analysis I) and the

following additional topics: Casorati-Weierstrass Theorem,

infinite products of analytic functions, normal families of

analytic functions.
title: Complex Analysis I (S)
